# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#   └ type: feat|fix|docs|style|refactor|perf|test|build|ci|chore|revert
#   └ scope: optional area of the codebase (e.g. api, build, web)
#   └ subject: imperative mood, no trailing period, ≤50 chars
#
# Examples:
#   feat(api): add bellows ignition endpoint
#   fix(build): pin dependency-management plugin to 1.1.7
#
# --- Body (wrap at 72) --------------------------------------------------
# Explain WHAT changed and WHY (not how). Blank line separates it from
# the subject above.
#
#
# --- Footer -------------------------------------------------------------
# Reference issues and breaking changes, e.g.:
#   Closes #123
#   Refs #456
#   BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
